      "content": "Interesting. So you're saying the shift toward collectivism or group-based identity could essentially replace the meritocratic foundation of the US? Some people argue this is leading to a sort of \"replacement\" of the original political identity of the country. Do you think this shift is an inevitable way that more diverse populations change the core character of a nation?",
